# Project Stack & Architecture

Definitive references:
- `docs/tech-stack.md` — libraries, versions, module dependencies
- `docs/architecture.md` — packages, data flow, database schema
- `docs/adr/001-kotlin-compose-stack.md` — decision record

## Accepted stack (do not substitute)

| Concern | Technology |
|---------|------------|
| UI | Jetpack Compose + Material 3 |
| Modules | `:domain` / `:application` / `:data` / `:app` |
| DB | Room + SQLite + FTS5 |
| Sync | WorkManager + OkHttp + Jsoup |
| Parser | Streaming XLSX (custom); POI test-only |
| DI | Hilt |
| Tests | JUnit 5 + MockK + Turbine |

## Layer rules (strict)

- `:domain` — pure Kotlin, zero Android/framework deps
- `:application` — use cases only, depends on `:domain`
- `:data` — Room, OkHttp, parser, workers; depends on `:domain`
- `:app` — Compose + ViewModels; calls use cases, never DAOs directly

## Before implementing

1. Use case must exist in `docs/use-cases/`
2. Domain terms must match `docs/glossary.md`
3. Domain tests written first (TDD, 90%+ coverage target)
4. All UI strings via i18n keys (`en` default, `pt-BR`)

